<div class="container">
    <h1>Profile page</h1>
    <p>Each PartyPlaylist profile has a public name to guarantee anonymity. This name will be visible to all PartyPlaylist users. To find your friends, ask them to share their public names. Or, if you’d like to update your public name to something more recognizable, feel free to make edits below.</p>
    <form method="POST" action="/profile" class="update-public-name">
        <label for="">Public name:</label><br>
        <input type="text" name="public-name" id="publicName" value="<%= user.displayName %>">
        <input class="waves-effect waves-light btn" type="submit" value="Update">
    </form>

    <h3>Delete my PartyPlaylist profile!</h3>
    <p>If you’re done using PartyPlaylist and want to delete your profile, click the button below. Just be aware that <span class="underline">deleting a profile is permanent.</span> There is no undo.</p>
    <a href="/profile" class="waves-effect waves-light btn delete-profile-link">Delete Account</a>
</div>

